snippet.title: openHV (OpenRA-Mod) - selfmade map testrun (A.I Battle)
snippet.description:
Here's a map i've made via the build in map editor openhv/openra offers.

It's called "Waterbridgeworld" for obvious reasons.



You can download the map here:
https://resource.openra.net/maps/42064/


There's a version without the bridges too:
https://resource.openra.net/maps/42062/


Enjoy the show.
